{"tid":658505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Maps 加入 AR 街景導航","createTime":"2018-05-09T04:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T23:43:27.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"507d442e1ce87f91fa1712a176bed52ec5cf009e","tid":658505,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"Google 在香港時間凌晨舉行的 I/O 大會上公布 Google Maps 地圖的重大更新。當中最重點功能有活用到 AR 擴增實境的 Street View 街景模式，幫你實時指引路向。另有「For you」根據用戶喜好而度身訂造的地圖位置／商戶推介功能，以及將多個位置分享給朋友並讓他們投票的新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcuoNn9W4AETdr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcuoNn9W4AETdr8.jpg&h=c8b4cc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n活用 AR 在相機畫面指引正確方向<br />\nGoogle I/O 大會上公布了關於 Google Maps 地圖的數項重點新功能。當中最受注目的是活用到 AR (Augmented Reality) 擴增實境的街景功能，利用到智能手機的鏡頭，在現實世界的畫面上，實時顯示出前往目的地之正確行走方向。用戶只要將鏡頭對準街道，Google Maps 就會在畫面上實時顯示出箭頭。畫面下方亦會顯示出地圖，顯示出導航資訊。用戶毋須購買任何 AR 裝置，配合一般手機鏡頭就可用到。 <br />\n<br />\n而除了指引方向外，新 AR 模式亦可協助用戶辨別鄰近位置，在相機鏡頭中顯示出商戶或景點，告訴你相機鏡頭中是甚麼建築物。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcuoNz4X0AEm7ui.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcuoNz4X0AEm7ui.jpg&h=146aaa08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle 還正開發一個虛擬導遊功能，一隻小動物將帶領用戶前往目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcuoN_iW4AIMqjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcuoN_iW4AIMqjD.jpg&h=4368fd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「For You」按用戶喜好推介鄰近商戶<br />\nGoogle 地圖會新增「For You」按用戶喜好而設的地點推介功能，例如用戶曾經投票喜歡吃拉麵，而不喜歡吃燒烤，又或者曾儲存大量火窩店，系統就會根據你的喜好，顯示出鄰近地點的推介商戶或地點。<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.news.livedoor.com/newsimage/stf/3/5/3519a_88_c9062186126130dd6dfa622779c8b693.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.news.livedoor.com%2Fnewsimage%2Fstf%2F3%2F5%2F3519a_88_c9062186126130dd6dfa622779c8b693.jpg&h=52fb97f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f80bb3e35295f444adaf9178c342ec35f9a7d4a9","tid":658505,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175a53dc78e353e3322a2317f397118805857942","tid":658505,"uid":57410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"比唔識睇地圖既弱智岩晒"},{"pid":"e969a7e83117cf12f41230b6615c0bbe6245a05f","tid":658505,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:43:27.000Z","msg":"點解要用firefox帶路?"}]}